    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinium: A Spaceboy's Tale is a classic, 2D platform adventure game with arcade elements. You follow a captivating story of a young boy named Leo, who set out on the journey of a lifetime. Accompany him, fulfil his dreams and fight hostile creatures while discovering diverse lands of the solar system.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore various environments</strong>  <br>Traverse across multiple planets and defeat unique enemies. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/90cbfd296e81bf7de11ada24e9ab0ac8.poster.avif?t=1770321815\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/90cbfd296e81bf7de11ada24e9ab0ac8.webm?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/90cbfd296e81bf7de11ada24e9ab0ac8.mp4?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master the art of platforming movement</strong><br>Enjoy a simple, yet satisfying character movement model, which over time is enhanced by new skills, such as dash, jetpack or double jump. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/bc87342439e662d2643837f33c644fc5.poster.avif?t=1770321815\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/bc87342439e662d2643837f33c644fc5.webm?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/bc87342439e662d2643837f33c644fc5.mp4?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fly your spaceship</strong><br>Old-school and fun mini-game where you steer a spaceship.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/006dbaa7fcf4d44c83e1b76154ff7790.poster.avif?t=1770321815\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/006dbaa7fcf4d44c83e1b76154ff7790.webm?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/006dbaa7fcf4d44c83e1b76154ff7790.mp4?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complex tale of Leo</strong> <br>A fascinating, linear story complemented by dialogues, music and cutscenes.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/14a5190db72ada380bff4db143cbce4a.poster.avif?t=1770321815\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/14a5190db72ada380bff4db143cbce4a.webm?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/14a5190db72ada380bff4db143cbce4a.mp4?t=1770321815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
